---
title: Schedule a Conversation.
description: Get in touch for individual coaching, team coaching, workshops, offsites, or leadership programs.
keywords: executive coach, leadership coach, teach coach, group coach.
image: "og/og-base.png"
layout: content
---


<section class="content">
  <div class="col-1">
    <p>Let’s talk! Tell me a bit about you, what you’re looking for, and what you want to be different in your world. I do my best to respond to all inquiries within 48 hours.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Updated by Claude Code - 2026-03-07 -->
   <div class="col-2">
     <form name="contact" method="POST" action="/thank-you" data-netlify="true"
 data-netlify-honeypot="bot-field" class="contact-form">
       <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact">
       <p class="contact-honeypot">
         <label>Don't fill this out: <input name="bot-field"></label>
       </p>

       <div class="form-field">
         <label for="name">Name <span class="required">*</span></label>
         <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
       </div>

       <div class="form-field">
         <label for="email">Email <span class="required">*</span></label>
         <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
       </div>

       <div class="form-field">
         <label for="pronouns">Pronouns</label>
         <input type="text" id="pronouns" name="pronouns">
       </div>

       <div class="form-field">
         <label for="location">Location <span class="required">*</span></label>
         <input type="text" id="location" name="location" required>
       </div>

       <div class="form-field">
         <label for="engagement">What type of engagement are you interested in? <span
 class="required">*</span></label>
         <select id="engagement" name="engagement" required>
           <option value="" disabled selected>Select an option</option>
           <option value="Executive Coaching">Executive Coaching</option>
           <option value="Team Coaching">Team Coaching</option>
           <option value="Coaching: Single Session">Coaching: Single Session</option>
           <option value="Leadership Programs">Leadership Programs</option>
           <option value="Offsites and Workshops">Offsites and Workshops</option>
           <option value="Something Else!">Something Else!</option>
         </select>
       </div>

       <div class="form-field">
         <label for="brings-you">What brings you to contact me at this moment in time?
 <span class="required">*</span></label>
         <textarea id="brings-you" name="brings-you" rows="6" required></textarea>
       </div>

       <div class="form-field">
         <label for="challenge">What is the biggest challenge or question in front of
 you? <span class="required">*</span></label>
         <textarea id="challenge" name="challenge" rows="6" required></textarea>
       </div>

       <div class="form-field">
         <label for="six-months">Imagine yourself 6 months from now—in what ways has
 your world changed? What is different? And what is still the same? <span
 class="required">*</span></label>
         <textarea id="six-months" name="six-months" rows="6" required></textarea>
       </div>

       <div class="form-field">
         <input type="submit" value="Let's Talk!">
       </div>
     </form>
   </div>
 </section>
